            <title>[SPARK-25578] Update to Scala 2.12.7</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-25578</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We should use Scala 2.12.7 over 2.12.6 now, to pick up this fix. We ought to be able to back out a workaround in Spark if so.&lt;/p&gt;

