                            <comment id="16633964" author="srowen" created="Mon, 1 Oct 2018 13:02:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=sadhen&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;sadhen&quot;&gt;sadhen&lt;/a&gt; I got this failure from &lt;tt&gt;QueryTest&lt;/tt&gt; with Scala 2.12.7, after removing what I believed was your workaround for this Scala issue:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&#160; == Results ==

&#160; !== Correct Answer - 1 == &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; == Spark Answer - 1 ==

&#160; !struct&amp;lt;array(100, 100):array&amp;lt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt; &#160; struct&amp;lt;percentile_approx(100.0, array(0.9, 0.9), 10000):array&amp;lt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;double&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;

&#160; ![WrappedArray(100, 100)] &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; [WrappedArray(100.0, 100.0)] (QueryTest.scala:163)&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Is that something we expected to be fixed, or maybe I misunderstood?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It passes with 2.12.7, without undoing your change.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16634111" author="apachespark" created="Mon, 1 Oct 2018 14:46:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;User &apos;srowen&apos; has created a pull request for this issue:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/spark/pull/22600&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/spark/pull/22600&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16634492" author="dongjoon" created="Mon, 1 Oct 2018 19:06:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=srowen&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;srowen&quot;&gt;srowen&lt;/a&gt;. Could you update the `Type` and `Priority` because we don&apos;t allow `Minor` and `Improvement` JIRA lands on `branch-2.4`?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16634533" author="srowen" created="Mon, 1 Oct 2018 19:45:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;OK. I&apos;m proposing it for 2.4.0 mostly because it &lt;em&gt;might&lt;/em&gt; be a bug fix, given &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=sadhen&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;sadhen&quot;&gt;sadhen&lt;/a&gt;&apos;s comment. As far as I can tell it&apos;s not breaking 2.4, but, according to the Scala release the change was to support 2.4. Maybe that overstated things, but might be less confusing to get this one in if we have another RC.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16634854" author="srowen" created="Tue, 2 Oct 2018 02:35:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Issue resolved by pull request 22600&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/spark/pull/22600&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/spark/pull/22600&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
